1:18:50.851 --> 1:18:53.968
Choose. Pick your poison.

1:18:55.481 --> 1:18:56.971
You said you'd do anything.

1:18:57.149 --> 1:18:59.561
I am giving you the opportunity to prove it.

1:19:00.736 --> 1:19:02.272
I can't.

1:19:02.446 --> 1:19:04.107
I can't, I'll die.

1:19:04.281 --> 1:19:06.533
No, you might die.

1:19:06.700 --> 1:19:08.565
Then again, you might not.

1:19:08.744 --> 1:19:10.075
Choose.

1:19:10.246 --> 1:19:14.205
Or I swear to God, you son of a bitch,
I will choose for you.

1:19:16.127 --> 1:19:18.163
- Fine.
- Wait, wait, wait, wait.

1:19:18.337 --> 1:19:20.999
I am giving you a chance, Tommy.

1:19:21.173 --> 1:19:23.084
That is something my wife never had.

1:19:23.259 --> 1:19:25.875
Now, you choose a bottle,
or I will choose the gun.

1:19:26.053 --> 1:19:30.092
Bottle gives you a 50-50 chance,
the gun gives you zero.

1:19:33.477 --> 1:19:34.853
(COCKS GUN)

1:19:35.104 --> 1:19:36.765
- OK. OK.
- Choose.

1:19:36.939 --> 1:19:40.181
- OK, I'll do it.
- One...

1:19:42.862 --> 1:19:44.102
Two!

1:19:46.449 --> 1:19:49.316
That's it. Drink up.

1:20:02.840 --> 1:20:05.456
(GROANING)

1:20:24.195 --> 1:20:26.186
(LAUGHING)

1:20:36.123 --> 1:20:39.365
Looks like my Iuck's changing.

1:20:42.630 --> 1:20:44.370
Not quite.

1:20:48.594 --> 1:20:52.052
What the fuck are you doing?
You said I had a chance!

1:20:52.223 --> 1:20:54.430
You said I had a chance!

1:20:59.480 --> 1:21:01.391
(SCREAMS)

1:21:03.776 --> 1:21:06.609
(SCREAMING)

1:21:19.083 --> 1:21:20.914
SARAH:
Nick.

1:21:21.752 --> 1:21:24.334
Nick, come on. Nick!

1:21:26.048 --> 1:21:27.208
Ah, damn.

1:21:33.889 --> 1:21:36.346
- Are you OK?
- HELLER: Hey, welcome back, Nick.

1:21:36.517 --> 1:21:38.303
Just in time for the final round.

1:21:40.187 --> 1:21:41.768
What the fuck?

1:21:47.861 --> 1:21:49.943
We're taking a little ride
down memory lane.

1:21:50.114 --> 1:21:53.106
A ride that ends the same way
that my dear Diana's did.

1:21:54.577 --> 1:21:55.942
Heller, stop.
You don't have to do this.

1:21:56.120 --> 1:21:57.360
Of course I do, Nick.

1:21:57.538 --> 1:22:00.325
You know, you've been a really,
really good sport tonight.

1:22:00.499 --> 1:22:03.081
Unfortunately for all of us,
the game's about to end.

1:22:03.252 --> 1:22:04.583
None of us are gonna win this one.

1:22:15.723 --> 1:22:17.213
You were never gonna turn yourself in.

1:22:17.391 --> 1:22:21.304
(CHUCKLING) Sorry about that, pal,
but justice must be served.

1:22:21.478 --> 1:22:25.266
Justice? This is your idea ofjustice?
Killing an innocent woman?

1:22:25.441 --> 1:22:26.931
Sarah has nothing to do with any of this.

1:22:27.109 --> 1:22:29.566
Yeah, neither did my wife!

1:22:29.945 --> 1:22:31.481
Tell you something, Nick.

1:22:31.655 --> 1:22:35.113
The system is broken,
and it can be manipulated by those in power.

1:22:36.827 --> 1:22:41.867
We are very, very lucky that your father
found a judge that will work with us.

1:22:42.833 --> 1:22:45.040
Twelve months rehab.

1:22:46.629 --> 1:22:48.540
ROBERTA:
You're gonna be a free man.

1:22:52.801 --> 1:22:54.507
The scales.

1:22:54.678 --> 1:22:56.054
(BUZZER SOUNDS)

1:23:02.269 --> 1:23:04.851
He said something about scales.
That they were out of whack.

1:23:05.022 --> 1:23:08.640
- Is it true?
- NICK: And I'd help him rebalance them.

1:23:09.568 --> 1:23:13.060
The only justice that we have
is the ones we make for ourselves.

1:23:13.238 --> 1:23:15.524
This isn'tjustice, this is murder.

1:23:16.450 --> 1:23:19.487
Damn. This makes you
exactly like Tommy.

1:23:19.662 --> 1:23:24.031
Hey! I am nothing like him!
I am not like him.

1:23:24.208 --> 1:23:26.039
(ENGINE REWING, TIRES SQUEALING)

1:23:30.964 --> 1:23:34.923
- Looks the same to me, man.
- Yeah? Well, let me prove it to you.

1:23:37.596 --> 1:23:38.802
WOMAN:
Emergency services, how can I help?

1:23:38.972 --> 1:23:41.008
- Help!
- Shut the fuck up!

1:23:41.183 --> 1:23:42.969
You listen very carefully to me.

1:23:43.143 --> 1:23:46.476
In the next few minutes, there is going
to be a rather horrific accident

1:23:46.647 --> 1:23:49.730
that's gonna take place
at the intersection of Sherwood and Grant.

1:23:49.900 --> 1:23:51.686
I suggest you get ambulances there now.

1:23:51.860 --> 1:23:54.727
- Help!
- Shut up! Huh?

1:23:54.905 --> 1:23:59.319
See, Nick? Huh? Ijust gave you
a better chance than my wife ever had.

1:23:59.493 --> 1:24:02.200
- You happy now?
- Go fuck yourself!

1:24:02.996 --> 1:24:06.534
Sweetheart, that is exactly
what I intend to do.

1:24:16.760 --> 1:24:20.719
Well, this is it, Nick.
Huh, the big finale.

1:24:20.889 --> 1:24:23.426
And even though the ambulances are coming,

1:24:23.600 --> 1:24:27.434
I'd say it's time
we end our game with a bang.

1:24:29.440 --> 1:24:31.556
Look at you. How you feeling, Nick?

1:24:31.734 --> 1:24:32.849
Diana!

1:24:33.026 --> 1:24:35.984
You're about to lose everything, and
you're powerless to do anything about it.

1:24:36.155 --> 1:24:40.489
But at least I'll give you a chance.
A chance to say goodbye to your wife.

1:24:40.659 --> 1:24:42.866
You have three minutes.

1:24:43.036 --> 1:24:44.697
You're pathetic.

1:24:44.872 --> 1:24:48.456
You think this is the kind of man your wife
wanted you to become? A murderer?

1:24:48.625 --> 1:24:52.209
HELLER: No, I think she would agree
that this is justice.

1:24:52.379 --> 1:24:54.586
The justice she never had.

1:24:54.757 --> 1:24:58.090
Maybe you'll get lucky, Nick.
Maybe you'll get lucky,

1:24:58.260 --> 1:25:00.922
and there'll be a good Samaritan
who just happens to be

1:25:01.096 --> 1:25:03.508
in the right place at the right time!

1:25:04.099 --> 1:25:05.885
Fuck you.

1:25:41.136 --> 1:25:43.343
No. Please, Nick.

1:25:44.139 --> 1:25:46.004
Please.

1:25:57.653 --> 1:26:01.646
One question. What would you have done
to save your wife's life?

1:26:03.116 --> 1:26:04.367
Anything.

1:26:05.494 --> 1:26:07.155
Exactly.

1:26:09.748 --> 1:26:11.739
Nick! Grab the gun!

1:26:13.502 --> 1:26:15.709
(TIRES SCREECHING)

1:26:21.677 --> 1:26:24.419
Nick! Stop him!

1:26:30.060 --> 1:26:31.470
No!

1:26:39.653 --> 1:26:41.484
SARAH:
Stop, please!

1:26:48.829 --> 1:26:51.411
(SIREN WAILING)

1:26:57.963 --> 1:26:59.703
(SHOUTS INDISTINCTLY)

1:26:59.882 --> 1:27:00.871
No!

1:27:15.022 --> 1:27:16.228
Duck, baby!

1:27:43.634 --> 1:27:44.999
Nick!

1:27:54.728 --> 1:27:56.013
Diana.

1:28:14.331 --> 1:28:16.572
(SIRENS WAILING)

1:28:21.338 --> 1:28:24.830
- You OK?
- I'm... I'm fine. Are you OK?

1:28:25.008 --> 1:28:26.544
Yeah.

1:28:41.441 --> 1:28:44.683
MCKENZIE:
It's over. Thank you.

1:29:03.672 --> 1:29:05.663
(DISTANT SIRENS WAILING)

1:34:09.394 --> 1:34:10.224
English - US - PSDH
